<沿革內容><![CDATA[1.Enacted on September 29, 2007 in accordance with the Bureau of National Health Insurance Order Chien-Pao-Chi-0960054756
2.Amended “Service Fee Standards for Requesting Insurance Information and Data from the BNHI” and re-entitled to “Fee-charging Standards for Requesting Data from the Bureau of National Health Insurance, Department of Health, Executive Yuan” on December 4 2009 in accordance with the Bureau of National Health Insurance Order Chien-Pao- Chi-0980092561
3.Amended on 30 July 2010 in accordance with the Bureau of National Health Insurance, Department of Health, Executive Yuan Order Chien-Pao-Chi-Tze No. 0990080248
4.Amendment of “Fee-charging Standards for Requesting Data from the Bureau of National Health Insurance, Department of Health, Executive Yuan,” Order Chien-Pao-Chi No. 1000077725, July 29, 2011 by the Bureau of National Health Insurance, Department of Health, Executive Yuan; the name shall be changed to “Fee-charging Standards for Requesting Data from the Insurer of National Health Insurance.”
